belcard
------------------------------------------
Belcard is a C++ library to manipulate VCard standard format.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  libbctoolbox1-5.4.116-1bl1
  libbelcard-devel-5.4.117-1bl1
  libbelcard1-5.4.117-1bl1
  libbelr1-5.4.117-1bl1
  libgcc1-13.4.0-1
  libstdc++6-13.4.0-1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46-1
  cmake-4.2.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-13.4.0-1
  libbctoolbox-devel-5.4.116-1bl1
  libbelr-devel-5.4.117-1bl1
  ninja-1.13.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/BelledonneCommunications/belcard

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/BelledonneCommunications/belcard/archive/refs/tags/5.4.117.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack belcard-5.4.117-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./belcard-5.4.117-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/belcard-5.4.117-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/belcard-5.4.117-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libbelcard1-5.4.117-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libbelcard-devel-5.4.117-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

